    schema1:description "Microcornea-corectopia-macular hypoplasia syndrome is characterised by microcornea, which may also be accompanied by corectopia and macular hypoplasia. It has been described in three individuals from two successive generations of one family."@en .

wd:Q55786411 a med:Disease ;
